metadata.name: Toonymania Meta World Cup 2022 Special Edition #1
metadata.description: The first Toonymania collaboration with Meta World Cup is The FIRST NFT collection based on results from live sporting events. Through each one of the Characters, in a funny and artistic way, we want to highlight the culture, costumes, ideology, and diversity of each one of the countries participating in the World Cup; while at the same time supporting mental health causes and promoting our love and passion for soccer.
